{"tid":143264,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"乜依家小學讀嘅嘢咁深嘅","createTime":"2017-03-04T13:17:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-07T10:37:28.000Z","uid":41052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"90f38ddf15918a89dcd09cc68efdda9cf398fd00","tid":143264,"uid":41052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T13:17:59.000Z","msg":"自問自己都唔係脫離讀書時期好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我個小四嘅啊妹嘅常識原來要讀好多嘢<br />\n肌肉 骨骼 神經系統 泌尿系統 消化系統&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想當年好似中學先接觸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算小學都只係學下有咩內臟嗰啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n難怪越黎越大壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93c719eafdc48442a46362b2bf1efc53d50f742c","tid":143264,"uid":30250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T20:30:45.000Z","msg":"咩呀我小四都有讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申而家year1"},{"pid":"ea8afe86fee9c45c95e97cd208e8b343e829aca6","tid":143264,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T22:21:41.000Z","msg":"父母總係覺得仔女學既野深過佢地以前"},{"pid":"bae8e58ee706734810cf7ec27e9be15fda81a857","tid":143264,"uid":8308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T10:37:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>父母總係覺得仔女學既野深過佢地以前</blockquote><br />\n事實上真係深左多左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前細個放學返歸通常都係做半個鐘功課<br />\n多既一兩個鐘都搞掂<br />\n<br />\n而家我表弟小三，未計課後班補習班<br />\n晚晚都做兩個鐘功課<br />\n唔好話落街踢波，睇多啦a夢都冇時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}